{"tid":469534,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"雙十一淘寶買左部跑步機 想小小野想問巴絲們(最好有買過跑步機既巴打入黎)","createTime":"2017-11-15T11:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T15:47:13.000Z","uid":119080,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b827672a183003080b2a62db1dc54c0a6d59d4ed","tid":469534,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟雙十一淘左部跑步機<br />\n想上黎問下CHING們的意見<br />\n<br />\n想買黎諗住係屋企跑步減肥用<br />\n<br />\n但係有運輸物流問題同跑帶尺寸大小合唔合適既問題想問下大家<br />\n<br />\n我選左既係呢一部<br />\n貪佢部機黑色 似GYM房FEEL<br />\n<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.13.5a57fc355RVYNI&amp;id=527573904054&amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;abbucket=7&amp;skuId=3455776492422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.13.5a57fc355RVYNI%26id%3D527573904054%26cm_id%3D140105335569ed55e27b%26abbucket%3D7%26skuId%3D3455776492422&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f0f417b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.13.5a57fc355RVYNI&amp;id=527573904054&amp;cm_id=140105335569ed55e27b&amp;abbucket=7&amp;skuId=3455776492422</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/j12775201711153022c81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fj12775201711153022c81.jpg&h=33e20b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m2015201711153140r81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm2015201711153140r81.jpg&h=9dc42291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m53178201711153125z81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm53178201711153125z81.jpg&h=6eec3732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸物流問題方面<br />\n買家客服話佢地用中鐵物流送到新界上水既倉再由我自取<br />\n$150RMB<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/f31976201711151447v81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Ff31976201711151447v81.jpg&h=58dae7af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇其他方法 可以成部野由其它物流方式直接送上屋企?<br />\n例如集運 轉運之類 (呢D方法亂UP 淘寶新手勿插)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跑帶尺寸大小合唔合適既問題方面<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v25443201711153536s81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv25443201711153536s81.jpg&h=d956f0ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/s7077201711153545w81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fs7077201711153545w81.jpg&h=7a8ebee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似張圖咁講部跑步機只有長126CMX寛45CM既跑帶範圍<br />\n<br />\n我身高174-175左右<br />\n腳掌長度27cm 著44-44.5號鞋 鞋底長度31cm左右<br />\n大腿連小腿長86-87cm左右<br />\n跑步機跑帶長126CM<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁既身型 腳掌長度 跑咁既跑道長度會唔會唔夠跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n計番鞋底既長度跑呢一部機 126/31=4.0645左右 <br />\n姐係條跑帶跑到4步多少少<br />\n有冇買過跑步機既師兄可以講下你地條跑帶幾大夠唔夠長同寛跑?<br />\n<br />\n我自己肩頭就43-44cm左右既 條跑帶既寛度就45CM<br />\n<br />\n咁既寛度size 我個人係部跑步機到揮手(跑步時上身揮肩動作)夠唔夠寛揮手?(我意思係舒服穩定咁持續跑到揮手)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9009D既解述圖:<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/a9737201711151308f81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fa9737201711151308f81.jpg&h=7536361a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一部機8008S既解述圖:<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/p13681201711151027f81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fp13681201711151027f81.jpg&h=f1b6f73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明同一間公司 2部跑步機解述圖講既野唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個話成年男子肩寛在40CM左右 一個話成年男子肩寛在45-48CM左右。<br />\n<br />\n跑帶越寛，運動時身體的撼擺幅空間越寛適，運動節奏更安全。<br />\n<br />\n8008S幅圖寫45CM-48CM係舒適型<br />\n適合身高在170CM以下及體重在120KG以下的大部份人群<br />\n<br />\n問過賣9009D既客服 佢既解答係咁:<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/s478201711152653i81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fs478201711152653i81.jpg&h=774f4bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己去個一間觀塘樓上實體店睇過一款機身長140 跑帶長1米 寛37cm既跑步機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.f1.page.auctions.yahoo.com/hk/auction/b20894661?u=tonykof2000&amp;actsrch=srp3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.f1.page.auctions.yahoo.com%2Fhk%2Fauction%2Fb20894661%3Fu%3Dtonykof2000%26actsrch%3Dsrp3&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=d769aeab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.f1.page.auctions.yahoo.com/hk/auction/b20894661?u=tonykof2000&amp;actsrch=srp3</a><br />\n呢部野成部走步機 行步機咁 跑得勁唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n想跑下呢部型號9009D 126CM長X45CM寛既跑帶岩唔岩我跑?<br />\n求師兄們解答下<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m39054201711155158s81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm39054201711155158s81.jpg&h=55587666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/b34503201711155211e81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fb34503201711155211e81.jpg&h=ebc35190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我睇過第二部跑步機跑帶尺寸有大小小既叫8008S<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/g42730201711155103g81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fg42730201711155103g81.jpg&h=c5c13cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/x10740201711155445a81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fx10740201711155445a81.jpg&h=0725c8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.28.5a57fc355RVYNI&amp;id=525951700506&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=7&amp;skuId=3207595057379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdetail.tmall.com%2Fitem.htm%3Fspm%3Da230r.1.14.28.5a57fc355RVYNI%26id%3D525951700506%26ns%3D1%26abbucket%3D7%26skuId%3D3207595057379&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=f8ca0f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://detail.tmall.com/item.htm?spm=a230r.1.14.28.5a57fc355RVYNI&amp;id=525951700506&amp;ns=1&amp;abbucket=7&amp;skuId=3207595057379</a><br />\n但係成機身成1米95咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/a25322201711155855q81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fa25322201711155855q81.jpg&h=eedaae55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過跑帶只有140cmx52cm<br />\n<br />\n我自已去度過physical同康文署既跑步機<br />\n個d既機身長19x cm左右 跑帶長15x cm寛5x cm<br />\n不過買呢d就無咩可能 實在太大了 又無得折曡 屋企應該擺唔落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望想買過跑步機既巴絲打可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6a087d02cef55bdcb25207673e76ae8d18311f","tid":469534,"uid":35693,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"淘寶預左閪架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n度咁多做乜"},{"pid":"46fc58e552c7b898939801a3d6709a526c913cae","tid":469534,"uid":139848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:53:48.000Z","msg":"都買咗喇 仲問條帶合唔合適有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb57db0bde6eb0c60f8f0aa97c19f9b3b9010d5","tid":469534,"uid":153796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:57:35.000Z","msg":"你好似已經買咗? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6572ea7a5ec51ccef234112f82ec026b718f2310","tid":469534,"uid":30910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:58:03.000Z","msg":"買完先問 戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211bf01f9b9d83e5eaa127e6238082e70c8849cd","tid":469534,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"呢個post開完一次又一次<br />\n樓主你收左佣金?"},{"pid":"6a318ad4ed0900200f94d9173609ba3e663d000f","tid":469534,"uid":72186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"死窮撚就咪咁多嗲啦"},{"pid":"43738856ea01adf788b23fd2e38ac9b64367b1a5","tid":469534,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"你條廢柴應該中學未畢業 加未做過運動 乜春都問"},{"pid":"1aaaa2431b77b123862889ada4cc53061b877f51","tid":469534,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買完先問 戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n客服話仲可以退既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都仲味叫佢運貨黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f43e8ad09787ad6f22f9ad403b867727a4455e6","tid":469534,"uid":119080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個post開完一次又一次<br />\n樓主你收左佣金?</blockquote><br />\n我見體育台 無乜聲氣試下潮流台開姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f440164c8ddc734f05b82d35560d57e7d5853625","tid":469534,"uid":51361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:18:24.000Z","msg":"我之前用企鵝集運運黎香港直接送到我屋企"},{"pid":"de21012682d94b2fe46e7e2a9886b24a5423066e","tid":469534,"uid":21522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"揾搬屋公司"},{"pid":"83fa9ade91b5faa25e8f03896ed05b3a7ad93e4b","tid":469534,"uid":1917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"你去gym room跑下度下夠唔夠寬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}